---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="GCC & Middle East | ARM Management"
  description="ARM Management's home market — company formation, transaction advisory, accounting, payroll, global mobility, and VARA crypto licensing across UAE, Saudi Arabia, Qatar, and the wider GCC."
>
<main>

  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="page-hero__bg" style="background-image:url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1512453979798-5ea266f8880c?w=1600&q=80&auto=format&fit=crop')"></div>
    <div class="page-hero__overlay"></div>
    <div class="page-hero__content container">
      <span class="eyebrow">GCC &amp; Middle East</span>
      <h1>GCC &amp; Middle East</h1>
      <p>UAE, Saudi Arabia, Qatar, Bahrain, Kuwait, and Oman.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--cream">
    <div class="container--narrow">
      <span class="eyebrow reveal">Overview</span>
      <h2 class="reveal">ARM Management in GCC &amp; Middle East</h2>
      <div class="gold-rule reveal"></div>
      <p class="reveal">The GCC is ARM Management's home market. We are headquartered in the UAE with deep operational experience across Dubai mainland, all major free zones, DIFC, and ADGM — as well as active practices across Saudi Arabia, Qatar, Bahrain, Kuwait, and Oman.</p>
      <p class="reveal" style="margin-top:20px">The UAE offers a uniquely compelling operating environment: zero personal income tax, a world-class financial infrastructure, the VARA virtual asset regulatory framework, and a UAE Golden Visa programme that provides long-term residency for investors, entrepreneurs, and talented professionals. For international businesses and investors, the UAE remains one of the most commercially attractive jurisdictions in the world.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--warm" style="border-top:1px solid #E2DDD6">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="eyebrow reveal">Services in GCC &amp; Middle East</span>
      <h2 class="reveal">What ARM Management Does Here</h2>
      <div class="gold-rule reveal"></div>
      <p class="reveal" style="color:#6B7280;margin-bottom:40px">All six ARM practice areas are available across the GCC &amp; Middle East. Click any service to learn more.</p>
      <div class="grid-3">
        <a href="/services/transaction-advisory" class="card reveal reveal-delay-1" style="text-decoration:none;display:block">
          <h3>Transaction Advisory</h3>
          <p>Cross-border M&amp;A, private investment, and deal structuring across the UAE, Saudi Arabia, and the wider GCC.</p>
          <span class="btn-secondary" style="margin-top:8px;display:inline-block">Learn More →</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/services/company-formation" class="card reveal reveal-delay-2" style="text-decoration:none;display:block">
          <h3>Company Formation</h3>
          <p>UAE mainland, DMCC, DIFC, ADGM, JAFZA, and all major free zones. Full lifecycle from entity selection to banking.</p>
          <span class="btn-secondary" style="margin-top:8px;display:inline-block">Learn More →</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/services/accounting-tax" class="card reveal reveal-delay-3" style="text-decoration:none;display:block">
          <h3>Accounting &amp; Tax</h3>
          <p>UAE corporate tax compliance, VAT registration and returns, and monthly bookkeeping for UAE mainland and free zone entities.</p>
          <span class="btn-secondary" style="margin-top:8px;display:inline-block">Learn More →</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/services/payroll-hr" class="card reveal reveal-delay-1" style="text-decoration:none;display:block">
          <h3>Payroll &amp; HR</h3>
          <p>UAE WPS-compliant payroll, employment contracts, and HR compliance for UAE mainland and free zone entities.</p>
          <span class="btn-secondary" style="margin-top:8px;display:inline-block">Learn More →</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/services/global-mobility" class="card reveal reveal-delay-2" style="text-decoration:none;display:block">
          <h3>Global Mobility</h3>
          <p>UAE Golden Visa — all categories including investor, entrepreneur, and talented professional. Family member inclusion.</p>
          <span class="btn-secondary" style="margin-top:8px;display:inline-block">Learn More →</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/services/crypto-web3" class="card reveal reveal-delay-3" style="text-decoration:none;display:block">
          <h3>Crypto &amp; Web3</h3>
          <p>VARA licence applications across all seven activity categories. Full VASP licensing from entity setup to operational licence.</p>
          <span class="btn-secondary" style="margin-top:8px;display:inline-block">Learn More →</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--navy">
    <div class="container--narrow">
      <span class="eyebrow reveal" style="color:#B8960C">Key Jurisdictions</span>
      <h2 class="reveal" style="color:#F7F3EC">Where We Operate</h2>
      <div class="gold-rule reveal"></div>
      <div style="margin-top:40px;display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:24px">
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-1" style="padding:24px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.05);border:1px solid rgba(184,150,12,.2);border-radius:2px">
          <h4 style="color:#B8960C;font-size:16px;margin-bottom:10px">UAE — Dubai &amp; Abu Dhabi</h4>
          <p style="color:rgba(247,243,236,.65);font-size:14px;line-height:1.75">Mainland, DMCC, DIFC, ADGM, JAFZA, and 40+ additional free zones. Zero personal income tax. VARA crypto licensing. Golden Visa.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2" style="padding:24px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.05);border:1px solid rgba(184,150,12,.2);border-radius:2px">
          <h4 style="color:#B8960C;font-size:16px;margin-bottom:10px">Saudi Arabia</h4>
          <p style="color:rgba(247,243,236,.65);font-size:14px;line-height:1.75">Company formation, investment advisory, and compliance support for Vision 2030 opportunities. MISA licences and joint venture structures.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-1" style="padding:24px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.05);border:1px solid rgba(184,150,12,.2);border-radius:2px">
          <h4 style="color:#B8960C;font-size:16px;margin-bottom:10px">Qatar</h4>
          <p style="color:rgba(247,243,236,.65);font-size:14px;line-height:1.75">QFC entity formation, investment advisory, and compliance for businesses operating in or entering the Qatari market.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2" style="padding:24px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.05);border:1px solid rgba(184,150,12,.2);border-radius:2px">
          <h4 style="color:#B8960C;font-size:16px;margin-bottom:10px">Bahrain, Kuwait &amp; Oman</h4>
          <p style="color:rgba(247,243,236,.65);font-size:14px;line-height:1.75">Market entry advisory, company formation, and ongoing compliance across the remaining GCC member states.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section">
    <h2 class="reveal">Begin Your GCC &amp; Middle East Expansion</h2>
    <p class="reveal reveal-delay-1">Speak with a senior ARM advisor about your requirements in GCC &amp; Middle East. We will give you an honest assessment of what is achievable, on what timeline, and at what cost.</p>
    <div class="btn-row reveal reveal-delay-2">
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Schedule a Consultation →</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</main>
</Base>
